text: Nasser Mohammed Ahmad Al-Jaber Al-Sabah (, born 22 December 1940) is a Kuwaiti politician. He was Prime Minister of Kuwait from 7 February 2006 until resigning on 28 November 2011. He is the first prime minister to date that never became ruler or even crown prince. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Kuwait
title: Nasser Al-Mohammed Al-Sabah
